714
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:24,170
Sincerity brings miracles.

715
00:38:34,020 --> 00:38:37,420
(Wei)

716
00:38:39,980 --> 00:38:40,860
My Lord,

717
00:38:41,170 --> 00:38:42,130
