739
00:39:23,170 --> 00:39:24,130
Of course,

740
00:39:24,340 --> 00:39:25,820
Manman is the smartest.

741
00:39:28,090 --> 00:39:29,300
Smart?

742
00:39:29,530 --> 00:39:30,860
She's just got a bit of wit.

743
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:35,690
